    "name": "AM Authentication System - Complete API Collection",
    "description": "Complete testing collection for all microservices\n\n**Base URLs:**\n- API Gateway: http://localhost:8000\n- User Management: http://localhost:8010\n- Auth Tokens: http://localhost:8001\n- Document Processor (Internal): http://am-document-processor:8070\n\n**Environment Variables:**\n- base_url: http://localhost:8000\n- user_url: http://localhost:8010\n- auth_url: http://localhost:8001\n- access_token: (set after login)\n- user_id: (set after registration)\n- process_id: (set after document upload)\n\n**New in this version:**\n✨ Document Processor endpoints added (Section 9 & 10)\n- Via API Gateway (protected, requires user JWT)\n- Direct access (public /types endpoint, internal network only)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
